'''洁净科技园'''（{{lang-en|'''CleanTech Park'''}}；[[首字母缩写|缩写]]：{{lang|en|'''CTP'''}}）） 是[[新加坡|新加坡]]第一座的商业生态园，由[[裕廊集团|裕廊集团]]开发建设。<ref name=house>{{cite press release|url=http://www.jtc.gov.sg/Newsroom/PressReleases/Pages/JTCandEDBunveil.aspx|title=Eco-Business Park to house a working population of 20,000 by 2030|publisher=JTC Corporation|date=2010-02-25|accessdate=2011-03-02|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20100301094122/http://www.jtc.gov.sg/Newsroom/PressReleases/Pages/JTCandEDBunveil.aspx|archivedate=2010-03-01}}</ref><ref name=launch>{{cite press release | url = http://www.jtc.gov.sg/Newsroom/PressReleases/Pages/20101011%28PR%29.aspx | title = Launch of CleanTech One, the First Multi-tenanted Building at CleanTech Park in Singapore | publisher = JTC Corporation | date = 2010-10-11 | accessdate = 2011-03-02 | archive-date = 2011-07-24 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20110724195748/http://www.jtc.gov.sg/Newsroom/PressReleases/Pages/20101011(PR).aspx | dead-url = yes }}</ref>其作用是为有兴趣在热带城市环境中测试和开发洁净新科技的企业提供一个聚集点，让他们能进行各种相关的研究。该生态园分三期建设，共计15座大楼，计划于2030年完全竣工。2010年10月，园区内第一座综合大楼CleanTech One竣工并交付使用，第二栋CleanTech Two与2014年开始投入使用。<ref name=launch/> 洁净科技园占地{{convert|50|ha|acre}}，紧临[[新加坡南洋理工大学|新加坡南洋理工大学]]，未来二者将作为该校的扩建计划进行整合，并作为新加坡政府规划的裕廊创新区的一部分。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.todayonline.com/Singapore/EDC110208-0000194/A-mini-city-growing-in-a-campus | title = A Mini-city Growing in a Campus | publisher = [[Today_(Singapore_newspaper)|Today]] | date = 2011-02-08 | accessdate = 2011-03-02 | last = Othman | first = Zul | archive-date = 2012-06-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120609142634/http://www.todayonline.com/Singapore/EDC110208-0000194/A-mini-city-growing-in-a-campus | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://zpolitics.zaobao.com.sg/zpolitics/news/story20160408-602425 | title = 除了南大和洁净科技园 裕廊创新区将涵盖登加 武林 峇哈 | publisher = [[联合早报|联合早报]] | date = 2016-04-08 | accessdate = 2016-11-07 | 6 =  | archive-date = 2019-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190927021830/http://zpolitics.zaobao.com.sg/zpolitics/news/story20160408-602425 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

